平方米<br />\n<br />\n參照港大嘅標準一平方米企2.5個人<br />\n龍頭2:40出發，4:00到金鐘，用時80分鐘，龍尾大概10:30到，頭尾共470分鐘，就當平均行完嘅時間係龍頭嘅兩倍<br />\n<br />\n所以估計人數係：<strong>205568平方米x2.5人x(470/160)次=1509640人</strong><br />\n<br />\n以上計法無計行人路、橫街、行咗其他內街、中途加入/離隊、金鐘加入<br />\n<br />\n所以200萬人真係好有可能"},{"pid":"0d24c7295ecf63e9b1828f54c3ce7a9852e7a603","tid":1253762,"uid":113326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc153217afb176400bed30f1bd1c3839ff6ba000","tid":1253762,"uid":226155,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T18:51:40.000Z","msg":"高峰時期要用4粒鐘行代表所有人都要用4粒鐘行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係中途插隊人數多先要4粒鐘，你估示威真係行三步一跪咁行咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以遊行人士步速為每秒20cm<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyoajR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyoajR.gif&h=f4f2b388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁明目張膽咁偷換概念無人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle map寫明40分鐘行完我當你遊行放慢用多一半時間（60分鐘）<br />\n就算用佢條算式<br />\n3000*20*6*8=288萬<br />\n<br />\n原來係因為計過數太大屈唔到先講行一程要四粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T19:21:51.000Z","msg":"我行左六個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e3f301523d1aed18d666adfec0c39015309625","tid":1253762,"uid":136744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6ea4679423602eea0d47eafdabf683352897c75","tid":1253762,"uid":112551,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T19:08:52.000Z","msg":"本報向兩名昨日身處遊行現場的學者查詢，兩名教授均不認同警方以最高峰期定點評估的人數作為推算基礎，